# Changelog

All notable changes to Dissect will be documented in this file.

## [1.0.0] - 2026-06-29

### Added
- Initial public release
- Passive web security scanning
- HTTP security header analysis
- Cookie security analysis
- Authentication surface detection
- HTML form analysis
- JavaScript-rendered DOM analysis using Playwright
- Executive security report
- Technical security report
- Responsive web interface
- Docker deployment support

### Fixed
- Playwright deployment compatibility on Railway
- Playwright deployment compatibility on Render
- JavaScript-rendered form detection improvements
